Package net.sf.sanity4j.workflow.tool

Interface Summary
ResultReader ResultReader provides a common interface which tool result readers must implement.
 

Class Summary
AbstractToolRunner AbstractToolRunner provides a properties-driven way of running external tools.
CheckStyleResultReader CheckStyleResultReader - Translates CheckStyle results into the common format used by the QA tool.
CheckStyleRunner CheckStyleRunner - a work unit that runs CheckStyle.
CoberturaMergeReader CoberturaMergeReader - The result of the Cobertura Merge doesn't require reading, therefore, this class does nothing.
CoberturaMergeRunner CoberturaMergeRunner - a work unit that merges Cobertura data files.
CoberturaReportRunner CoberturaReportRunner - a work unit that produces a Cobertura report.
CoberturaResultReader CoberturaResultReader - Translates cobertura results into the common format used by the QA tool.
FindBugsResultReader FindBugsResultReader - Translates FindBugs results into the common format used by the QA tool.
FindBugsRunner FindBugsRunner - a work unit that runs FindBugs.
Pmd4Runner PmdRunner - a work unit that runs PMD.
Pmd5Runner PmdRunner - a work unit that runs PMD 5.x.
PmdCpd4ResultReader PmdCpdResultReader - Translates PMD CPD results into the common format used by the QA tool.
PmdCpd4Runner PmdCpd4Runner - a work unit that runs PMD CPD.
PmdCpd5ResultReader PmdCpdResultReader - Translates PMD CPD 5.x results into the common format used by the QA tool.
PmdCpd5Runner PmdCpdRunner - a work unit that runs PMD CPD 5.x.
PmdCpdResultReader Deprecated. use PmdCpd4ResultReader
PmdCpdRunner Deprecated. use PmdCpd4Runner
PmdResultReader PmdResultReader - Translates PMD results into the common format used by the QA tool.
PmdRunner Deprecated. use Pmd4Runner
ToolRunnerGroup ToolRunnerGroup is responsible for running the tools to be used in the analysis.
